        <div class="mini-date">Redi Carpet &nbsp;|&nbsp; Sep 2024 &ndash; Dec 2024</div>
        <p class="mini-desc">Identified and eliminated redundant manual processes across Central and Midwest regions. Documented and enforced uniform workflows to drive consistency and speed across all branches.</p>
        <div class="mini-result">Order allocation time reduced to under 15 minutes; ~20% productivity gain</div>
      </div>

      <div class="mini-project">
        <div class="mini-type">Technology Rollout</div>
        <div class="mini-title">CRM &amp; Workflow Tool Implementation</div>
        <div class="mini-date">Redi Carpet &nbsp;|&nbsp; Nov 2022 &ndash; Jan 2023</div>
        <p class="mini-desc">Led a multi-department CRM and workflow tool rollout for 12 employees. Coordinated training schedules, stakeholder communication, and post-launch support with zero critical service disruptions.</p>
        <div class="mini-result">10% KPI improvement post-launch; zero critical disruptions</div>
      </div>

      <div class="mini-project">
        <div class="mini-type">Onboarding &amp; Vendor Management</div>
        <div class="mini-title">Subcontractor Onboarding Program</div>
        <div class="mini-date">Redi Carpet &nbsp;|&nbsp; Jan 2020 &ndash; Mar 2020</div>
        <p class="mini-desc">Designed a scalable onboarding framework for new subcontractors that reduced ramp-up time and directly supported regional growth by expanding network capacity.</p>
        <div class="mini-result">30% expansion in subcontractor network capacity</div>
      </div>

      <div class="mini-project">
        <div class="mini-type">Analytics &amp; Automation</div>
        <div class="mini-title">AI-Powered Reporting Solution</div>
        <div class="mini-date">Redi Carpet &nbsp;|&nbsp; Ongoing</div>
        <p class="mini-desc">Built operational dashboards using Power BI and Microsoft Copilot to deliver real-time visibility to leadership across 13+ branches, dramatically reducing manual report generation time.</p>
        <div class="mini-result">80%+ reduction in report generation time across all branches</div>
      </div>

      <div class="mini-project">
        <div class="mini-type">Workflow Redesign</div>
        <div class="mini-title">Invoice Correction Workflow Redesign</div>
